{"id":862,"date":"2023-01-06T12:32:58","date_gmt":"2023-01-06T12:32:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/?p=862"},"modified":"2023-01-07T06:57:29","modified_gmt":"2023-01-07T06:57:29","slug":"price-payment-plan-for-bahria-town-karachi-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/2023\/01\/06\/price-payment-plan-for-bahria-town-karachi-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Price &#038; Payment Plan for Bahria Town Karachi 2"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<header class=\"entry-header\">\n<div class=\"entry-meta row justify-content-between align-items-center\">\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>KARACHI:<\/strong> Bahria Town Karachi 2 will open bookings for residential and commercial plots on 5<sup style=\"color: #000000;\">th<\/sup> January 2023.<\/span><\/div>\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n<div><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" style=\"color: #000000;\" src=\"https:\/\/propakistani.pk\/proproperty\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Bahria-Town-Plot-Booking.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/propakistani.pk\/proproperty\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Bahria-Town-Plot-Booking.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/propakistani.pk\/proproperty\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Bahria-Town-Plot-Booking-400x224.jpg 400w, https:\/\/propakistani.pk\/proproperty\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Bahria-Town-Plot-Booking-768x430.jpg 768w\" alt=\"Bahria Town Booking\" width=\"640\" height=\"358\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/header>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-8 entry-content\">\n<div class=\"the-post-content\">\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">This is the second project by Bahria Town in Karachi and is currently in the developing stage.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bahria Town Karachi 2 has offered residential and commercial plots of different sizes and prices.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bahria Town Karachi 2 will be offering the following residential plots:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">125 Yards<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">250 Yards<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">500 Yards<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">1,000 Yards<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bahria Town Karachi 2 will be offering the following commercial plots:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">125 Yards<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">250 Yards<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bahria Town Karachi 2 will also be offering 3-bedroom Villas in the following plot size:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #000000;\">125 Yard<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">It has also been disclosed that the plots will be offered on a 4-year installment plan, and the booking price would be 15% of the total principal amount.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Additionally, the possession of plots would be granted within 2 years after booking.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The management of BTK2 has also disclosed that all the development charges would be included in the booking amount, and no additional amount would be charged.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bahria Town claims that the development work is being carried out at a rapid pace, and almost 40% of infrastructure work has been finished, including the main gate, mosque, hospital, school, and college.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">KARACHI:&nbsp;Bahria Town Karachi 2&nbsp;is now offering bookings for residential and commercial plots of various sizes.<\/span><\/p>\n<div class=\"code-block code-block-4 code-block-inpost-btf\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Customers can choose from residential plots ranging in size from 125 sq. yards to 1,000 sq. yards and commercial plots at 125 sq. yards and 250 sq. yards.<\/span><\/p>\n<h5><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Price Plan of Bahria Town Karachi 2<\/span><\/h5>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Below is the price and payment plan for Bahria Town Karachi Phase 2.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><a class=\"ari-fancybox\" style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"https:\/\/propakistani.pk\/proproperty\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Bahria-Town-Karachi-2-Price-Plan.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-8581 \" src=\"https:\/\/propakistani.pk\/proproperty\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Bahria-Town-Karachi-2-Price-Plan.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 818px) 100vw, 818px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/propakistani.pk\/proproperty\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Bahria-Town-Karachi-2-Price-Plan.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/propakistani.pk\/proproperty\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Bahria-Town-Karachi-2-Price-Plan-400x224.jpg 400w, https:\/\/propakistani.pk\/proproperty\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Bahria-Town-Karachi-2-Price-Plan-768x430.jpg 768w\" alt=\"Bahria Town Karachi 2 Price Plan\" width=\"818\" height=\"458\"><\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The plots are available on 4-year easy installment plans with down payments of 8-10% of the principal amount.<\/span><\/p>\n<div>\n<div><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span class=\"ctaText\">ALSO READ<\/span>&nbsp;<span class=\"postTitle\">Bahria Town Karachi Denies Claims of Heavy Rains Submerging the Society<\/span><\/span><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Upon making 50% of the payment, possession of the plot will be granted to the customer.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The attached&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/01\/Booking-form-saad-associates.pdf\"><strong>Bahria Town Booking Form<\/strong><\/a>&nbsp;requires complete information from the investor and includes the bank details for payment.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Furthermore, it is important to note that the society claims that 40% of the development work has been finished including the main gate, mosque, hospital, school, and college.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https:\/\/wa.me\/message\/AHM6HUWWKEJVC1\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"button alert box-shadow-5 box-shadow-5-hover\"  style=\"border-radius:99px;\">\n    <span>Book Now your property in BTK 2<\/span>\n  <\/a>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":869,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[144],"tags":[154,156,145,148,155,159,160,150,152,143,157,149,158,142,151,128,153],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/862"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=862"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/862\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":903,"href":"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/862\/revisions\/903"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/869"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=862"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=862"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/saadassociates.co\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=862"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}